GrammarNotions.ECFGNodes

Class CECFGAbstractListNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • Nodes.CNode
      • GrammarNotions.ECFGNodes.CECFGNode
        • GrammarNotions.ECFGNodes.CECFGAbstractListNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INode, INodeList
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CAltNode, CMultiDotNode, CPlusNode, CStarNode, CTupleNode

    public abstract class CECFGAbstractListNode
extends CECFGNode
implements INodeList
    CECFGAbstractListNode is an abstract class which defines the common part of star, plus, multidot and tuple nodes: - It descends from CECFGNode - It has a list of subtrees - It is the ancestor of CStarNode, CPlusNode, CMultiDotNode and CTupleNode DO NOT CONFUSE WITH THE NO LONGER USED CLASS CECFGNodeList
